This folder conatins the MQTT Publishing Clients (Python scripts) meant to be run on PCs and Single Board computers like Raspberry Pi.

-> Paho MQTT Client libraray is used used for the clients, so installation of Paho client libraray is a prerequisite for successfully running these scripts.
-> Mosquittu MQTT broker was used for these scripts.
-> User credentials and MQTT server address need to be changed in these scripts according to your broker and the level of security used.
